    "lyrics": {
      "text": "An-gel-ic Pow-ers were a-bove Thy tomb, and they that guard-ed Thee be-came as dead. And Mar-y stood by the grave seek-ing Thine im-mac-u--late Bod-y. Thou hast de-spoiled__ Ha-des and wast not tried there-by. Thou didst meet the Vir-gin and didst grant us__ life. O Thou Who didst a-rise from the dead, Lord,__ glo-ry be to__ Thee.__\n\nLord,__ glo-ry be to Thee.___"
    }
